cat << EOF
zathura is a highly customizable and functional PDF viewer based on the poppler
rendering library and the gtk+ toolkit. The idea behind zathura is
an application that provides a minimalistic and space saving interface as well
as an easy usage that mainly focuses on keyboard interaction.
